description:
The action story is set in Edo-era Tokyo in the early 1700s. The eighth shogun Tokugawa Yoshimune ordered boxes to be installed so commoners can submit their thoughts. After hearing their voices, the shogun creates a new magistrate unit — Mushibugyou — to protect the people in the heart of the city. Each member is a specialist with unique fighting skills.
Source: ANN

REGULAR.description:
Jinbei has traveled all the way to Edo to join the Insect Magistrate’s Office.  That is if he can find it before being killed by a Yarougumo.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Here Comes Tsukishima Jinbei!
Tsukishima Jinbee Iza Mairu!!!
月島仁兵衛 いざ参る!!!

REGULAR.description:
Teamed up Hibachi for his first assignment, he is regulated to the sidelines, forbidden to draw his sword.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: My Rival Is Female Ninja, Hibachi!
Rival wa Onna Ninja Hibachi!
ライバルは女忍者 火鉢!

REGULAR.description:
While on patrol, Jinbei can’t understand why the people of Edo hate Shungiku.  When Shungiku is accused of murder, Jinbei stands by his new sword master.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: The Killer of 99, Koikawa Shungiku!
Tsukumogiri Koikawa Shungiku!
九十九斬り 恋川春菊!

REGULAR.description:
The youngest member of the group, Ichinotani Tenma and his shikigami are very powerful, but even he has a fatal weakness that Jinbei is determined to help him overcome.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Ichinotani Tenma, Boku wa Dekiru Ko
Ichinotani Tenma, I Can Do It!
一乃谷天間 僕は出来る子

REGULAR.description:
A request from Minster Mizuno Saneyoshi has requested for Mugai to perform an insect extermination.  Mugai has picked Jinbei to accompany him, but won’t explain why…
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mugai: Kokou no Hitomi ga Ou Saki wa
Mugai: What Solitary Eyes See
無涯 孤高の瞳が追う先は

REGULAR.description:
A masked figure is stalking the headquarters of the Insect Brigade.  What does he want and why does he know so much about their inner workings?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Omen no Shita no Ikemen: Nagatomimaru
The Hot Guy Beneath the Mask: Nagatomimaru
お面の下のイケメン 長福丸

REGULAR.description:
Tsukishima runs around preparing for the famous Ryogoku River Opening, as everyone else evacuates for the best seat for Summer War.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Hana no Oedo no Natsu no Jin!!
Summer War in Edo!!
花のお江戸の夏の陣!!

REGULAR.description:
A former team member of Mugai has been tasked to gather information on the Insect Magistrate, she attaches to Jinbei as a source of info, learning this Mugai offers her some advice.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mitsuki no Honey Trap
Mitsuki`s Honey Trap
蜜月のお色気♥大作戦(ハニートラップ)

REGULAR.description:
The Insect Magistrate is in danger and all military groups must set out!  But as the groups set off a bug attacks Edo and Jinbei must decide to save the town or follow orders.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mushikari Kyoushuu!! Hachijoujima no Hen!!
The Insect Hunters Attack!! Battle of Hachijo Island!!
蟲狩強襲!!八丈島の変!!

REGULAR.description:
The Insect Magistrate is confused by Jinbei’s actions; is he friend or foe?  Jinbei continues his fight against the hunters but the difference in skill is obvious.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Kuroageha Arrives
Kuroageha Kourin
黒揚羽降臨

REGULAR.description:
Cornered by Sougan, the strongest of the Insect Hunters, attacks the Insect Magistrate but seconds before death an unfamiliar Jinbei awakens.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Jinbei`s Power Awakens!!
Mezameta Chikara: Jinbee, Kakusei!!
目覚めた力 仁兵衛, 覚醒!!

REGULAR.description:
Returning to Edo, the Insect squad is stunned to see mounds of bug carcasses and one man standing alone.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Chichi to no Shugyou! Fugaku Sanjuurokken!!
Training With Father! The Thirty-six Blades of Fuji!!
父との修行! 富嶽三十六剣!!

REGULAR.description:
Osono the journalist plans to write an expose about the Insect Magistrates and knows she will get her big scoop at the women’s bath.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: We`ll Show You Everything!! The Edo Women`s Baths!!
Zenbu Misemasu!! Oedo no Onnayu!!
全部見せます!!お江戸の女湯!!

REGULAR.description:
A mysterious insect man, Sarutobi Sasuke, appears in Edo.  The city is in danger but the City Patrol Group is nowhere to be found.  The Shrine and Samurai House patrol groups fight back, but are overwhelmed.  Just when everything seems lost to his speedy attacks...!?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Insect!? Man!? A Mysterious Enemy Attacks!
Mushi!? Hito!? Nazo no Teki, Shuurai!
蟲!? 人!? 謎の敵, 襲来!

REGULAR.description:
Sanada Yukimura`s 10 Crucifix Insects attack one village after another. The Insect Magistrate rushes to Edo Castle, where she discovers a secret in Nagatomimaru`s room.  And the secret past of Jinbei`s father Genjuro, and how he met Jinbei`s mother, is revealed!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Iza Kishuu e! Sanada Jikketsuchuu, Arawaru!
To Kishuu! The Ten Crucifix Insects of Sanada Appear!
いざ紀州へ! 真田十傑蟲, 現る!

REGULAR.description:
The Insect Magistrate heads to Kishuu to recover her lost powers.  Oooka Tadasuke, Edo`s smartest man, accompanies her as her guard.  Jinbei goes as well, but Oooka is upset by his failings as a Samurai.  And then Nezu Jinpachi, one of the 10 Crucifix Insects, appears!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Cool na Megane no Marubatsu Kouza
The Cool Guy in Glasses Lectures on Right and Wrong
クールなメガネの○×講座

REGULAR.description:
Jinbei is chased and captured by the people of Kishuu at the order of Sanada Yukimura.  The village of Iwamatsu, where he is kept, is attacked by bandits, and he wins the hearts of the people by chasing them off.  However, there is only a brief moment of rest.  Two of the ten crucifix insects, the Rokurou Combo, take a girl hostage!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Sanada Yukimura no Wana! Otazunemono Houimou!!
Sanada Yukimura`s Trap! Caught in a Net!!
真田幸村の罠! お尋ね者包囲網!!

REGULAR.description:
Jinbei heads to meet the lord of Kishuu, but he finds Hibachi instead.  The party meets with the rest of the City Patrol group and enjoys a brief rest.  But the time limit is drawing nigh, and just when the Ten Crucifix Insects attack the people of Kishuu...
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Kokugen no Toki: Mushibugyousho Kenzan!
Time`s Up! The Insect Magistrate`s Office Arrives!
刻限の時 蟲奉行所見参!

REGULAR.description:
The battle with the Ten Crucifix Insects begins!  The first round is Tsukishima Jinbei vs. Nedzu Jinpachi.  As soon a the battle begins Jinbei is drawn into the castle moat, and forced to fight underwater at a huge disadvantage.  Does Jinbei have a way to win? And what is the true form of the Ten Crucifix Insects!?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: He Shed His Skin!? The Insect-men`s True Form!!
Masaka no Dappi!? Mushibito no Shin no Sugata!!
まさかの脱皮!? 蟲人の真の姿!!

REGULAR.description:
The second battle of Wakayama Castle is against Kirigakure Saizou, the strongest of the Ten Crucifix Insects, who is a master of strange techniques.  Hibachi is dazzled and bewildered by illusions of her past.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Dream of the Butterfly
Kochou no Yume
胡蝶の夢

REGULAR.description:
The Miyoshi brothers have powerful regenerative capabilities.  They say that taking life is offering salvation, and in them Shungiku sees his own younger self.  Oooka, who knows the old Shungiku, is doubtful he can win the battle.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: G o Kirisaku Jiaigiri!!
Gを切り裂く慈合い斬り!!
The Compassion Slash That Cuts G!!

REGULAR.description:
The fourth battle of Wakayama Castle is between Ichinotani Tenma and Anayama Kosuke.  Anayama says "Justice" a lot.  He attacks Tenma with his warped sense of justice.  A badly wounded Tenma continues to fight, hoping for just one thing: to meet the father and mother he`s never seen.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Docchi ga Seigi!? Tenma to Justice
Who Is Righteous!? Tenma and Justice
どっちが正義!? 天間とジャスティス

REGULAR.description:
Jinbei`s flower team advances steadily.  Meanwhile the snow team, the Magistrate`s party, reaches the eternal well.  Kirigakure Saizou then reveals his true self and begins a one on one fight with Mugai.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: My Life`s Greatest Task
Waga Shougai de Ichiban no Otsutome
我が生涯で一番のお勤め

REGULAR.description:
The battle for Wakayama castle continues!  Muagi battles Saizou while the rest of the Magistrate`s fights the last of the crucifix insects, and Jinbei attacks Yukimura.  The Magistrate plunges herself into the Eternal Well, and her mysterious past is revealed.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mushibugyou Norowareshi Kako
The Insect Magistrate`s Cursed Past
蟲奉行 呪われし過去

REGULAR.description:
When he learns that the power of the well will cost the servant her memories, Jinbei goes into the well after her. She was prepared to lose her memories but Jinbei persuades her not to.  When she leaves, Sanada Yukimura is there...
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Kawashita Yakusoku wa Zetsubou no Naka no Kibou
The Promise Is Hope Within Despair
交わした約束は絶望の中の希望

REGULAR.description:
The well gives the Magistrate back her power and she transforms into Shiroageha, but her memories are lost.  She attacks Jinbei, and the power of the well makes Sanada much stronger.  Jinbei, who swore to fight until he dies, is faced with his last enemy.  The final battle begins!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Tsukishima Jinbee: Koko ni Ari!!!
Tsukishima Jinbei Is Here!!!
月島仁兵衞 ここにあり!!!
